          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"graph-rag-using-text2cypher\">Graph RAG using Text2Cypher</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">This is a demo app in marimo that allows you to query the Nobel laureate graph (that's managed in Kuzu) using natural language. A language model takes in the question you enter, translates it to Cypher via a custom Text2Cypher pipeline in Kuzu that's powered by DSPy. The response retrieved from the graph database is then used as context to formulate the answer to the question.</span>\n<blockquote>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">- Powered by Kuzu, DSPy and marimo -</span>\n</blockquote></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
